description: Hey!... You Gonna Eat or What? has been an Austin tradition since October. Serving iconic sandwiches with a Texas twist.Hey!... You Gonna Eat or What? is known for (among other things!) it's Shiner Bock beer-battered Monte Cristo - served with a hommemade Cherry & Fig jelly. Our permanent menu featurs 4 incredible sandwiches but don't be misled... Our menu of "Specials" always offers up a wide variety of cool, new looks. There's something for everybody!... (Well, everybody with impeccable taste, that is.)
name: Hey!... You Gonna Eat Or What?
